    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and high-revving internals. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone a comprehensive VANOS service and subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known stress points. Riding on a well-sorted suspension with crisp turn-in, it remains a benchmark for analog performance. Mechanically sound and ready for the apex.",
