    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a balance of performance and comfort that is hard to find. The exterior maintains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all tactile buttons and digital displays functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, a new air filter, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. With deep tread on the tires and firm, reliable braking, this car is ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable service. It is a complete package for someone seeking a well-cared-for vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
